data.eml:eml: Morphology of preimaginal stages and taxonomical relationship of Synanthedon spuleri (Fuchs, 1908) (Lepidoptera: Sesiidae) with closely related species in Central Europe

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bąkowski, Marek (2013): Morphology of preimaginal stages and taxonomical relationship of Synanthedon spuleri (Fuchs, 1908) (Lepidoptera: Sesiidae) with closely related species in Central Europe. Zootaxa 3666 (2): 194-202, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3666.2.5
